# Placeholder for node keys
# Keys should be generated using aegis-cli keygen
# DO NOT commit actual keys to version control
#
# Expected files per node:
#   - node{N}.dilithium.key  (Dilithium-III private key)
#   - node{N}.dilithium.pub  (Dilithium-III public key)
#   - node{N}.crt            (TLS certificate)
#   - node{N}.key            (TLS private key)
#
# Generate keys:
#   aegis-cli keygen --algorithm dilithium-iii --output node0
#
# Generate TLS certificates:
#   openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout node0.key -out node0.crt -days 365 -nodes
